The m2 converter takes source and reference sentences and create .m2 annotation. (Error types are not specified.)

1. prerequisites

- nltk
  pip install nltk
- pattern
  pip install pattern
- stanford pos tagger
  run sh getpostagger.sh

2. getAllM2.sh : an instance shell script for run all reference types
or run m2converter.py independently.

(e.g.) python m2converter.py -s  source_txt -r reference_dir > reference_in.m2

Questions?
  E-mail to keisuke@cs.jhu.edu
